data.description: Opportunity knocks.  FHA assumable loan at an amazing 2.75% interest rate.  Welcome home to your own little oasis in the heart of Northeast Austin! This completely remodeled single-story home offers a spacious corner lot with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1840 sqft of living space. Inside you'll find an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and wood beams that adds a rustic charm to the home. The kitchen is adorned with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and even a wine fridge for entertaining guests. Step out back onto the large covered patio overlooking your fenced-in yard offering plenty of space for any outdoor activities you can imagine. Other features include an HVAC system replaced in August 2019 as well as additional outbuildings on the property adding extra storage options.
